## 5. PAGE-BY-PAGE PRD

---

### 5.1 LOGIN PAGE

#### Layout
Two-column split — 50/50 on desktop, single column on mobile.

**Left Half — Brand Statement**

Large display text:
```
VENDORA.
PROCUREMENT,
COMMANDED.
```

Below the heading, one subline:
```
"Where every purchase decision lives."
```

**Right Half — Login Panel**

**Role Selector (top of panel):**

Four tiles in a 2×2 grid. Each tile shows:
- Icon (lucide-react)
- Role name
- One-line description

```
┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐
│  [UserCircle]    │  │  [Building2]     │
│  PROCUREMENT     │  │  VENDOR          │
│  OFFICER         │  │                  │
│  Create & track  │  │  Submit quotes & │
│  all purchases   │  │  track orders    │
└──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘

┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐
│  [CheckSquare]   │  │  [Settings]      │
│  MANAGER /       │  │  ADMIN           │
│  APPROVER        │  │                  │
│  Approve or      │  │  Manage system   │
│  reject orders   │  │  & analytics     │
└──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘
```

On clicking a role tile: credentials auto-fill below.

**Credential Fields:**
- Email input with auto-fill on role tile click
- Password input with eye toggle icon
- Login button: text `ENTER VENDORA →`

**Demo credentials strip (below button):**
```
▸ officer@vendora.com  ▸ vendor@vendora.com
▸ manager@vendora.com  ▸ admin@vendora.com
  password: demo123
```

