#### Layout: Full Width

**Urgency Banner (top, full width — shows if any pending approvals):**
```
⚡  3 APPROVALS WAITING — OLDEST IS 18 HOURS. REVIEW NOW →
```
Click → jumps to queue.

**Below Banner — Split View:**

Left 35% — Approval Queue:
```
● RFQ #2847 — ₹1,12,100    [18h pending]
● RFQ #2851 — ₹45,000      [6h pending]
● RFQ #2856 — ₹8,23,000    [1h pending]  HIGH VALUE ⚠
```
HIGH VALUE tag for anything > ₹5L.

Right 65% — Approval Detail Card (see 5.11):
Always showing the selected item. Switches instantly on left-panel click.

**Below the split — Manager Analytics (three charts):**

Chart 1 — Approval Velocity (line chart, Recharts):
Average hours from submission to approval, last 30 days.
Target line at 24h. If avg > 24h: `"You're averaging 31h. Target is 24h."`

Chart 2 — Spend by Category (horizontal bar chart, Recharts):
Each category = one horizontal bar, Space Mono values on right.

Chart 3 — Vendor Concentration Risk:
Horizontal bars showing % of spend per vendor.
> 30% = warning tag. > 50% = alert tag.

