### 5.11 MANAGER / APPROVER — APPROVAL DETAIL

*Embedded in Dashboard right panel, or full screen on mobile.*

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  RFQ #2847 — INDUSTRIAL BEARINGS                               │
│  250 units  │  Requested by: Ramesh Shah                       │
│                                                                │
│  SELECTED VENDOR:  Global Supplies   █████ 4.8★               │
│  QUOTED AMOUNT:    ₹1,12,100                                  │
│  DELIVERY:         9 days from PO date                        │
│  vs LOWEST QUOTE:  ₹95,000 (Sharma Traders)                   │
│  PRICE PREMIUM:    +₹17,100 (+18%)                           │
│                                                                │
│  WHY NOT THE CHEAPEST? ↓                                       │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │ Sharma Traders: 3.1★ · 8h response · 1 dispute          │  │
│  │ Global Supplies: 4.8★ · 1h response · 0 disputes        │  │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                                                │
│  OFFICER NOTE:                                                 │
│  "Global Supplies has never missed a deadline. Sharma          │
│   caused a 2-week delay last quarter."                        │
│                                                                │
│  NEGOTIATION THREAD: [VIEW 4 MESSAGES →]                      │
│  (link to the thread — manager can read the conversation)     │
│                                                                │
│  APPROVAL CHAIN:                                               │
│  ✓ Ramesh Shah (Officer)     Submitted Oct 12                  │
│  ⏳ Priya Mehta (You)         Pending                          │
│  ○ Finance Head               Not yet                          │
│                                                                │
│  YOUR REMARKS (required for rejection):                        │
│  [________________________________________________]           │
│                                                                │
│  [✗  REJECT]                       [✓  APPROVE  →]           │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Hold-to-Approve mechanic (for values > ₹1 lakh):**
- Button starts filled
- User holds mouse/finger down
- Circular SVG ring animates around the button, fills in 1.5 seconds
- On complete: triggers approval, button flashes green, success toast fires
- If released early: ring resets, button wobbles (CSS shake animation)
- Label during hold: `HOLD TO CONFIRM...`

**Rejection flow:**
- Click REJECT → remarks field becomes required (red outline if empty)
- Cannot submit rejection without remarks
- After rejection: red checkmark animation, officer gets instant notification with remarks

**Manager can also:**
- Click `VIEW 4 MESSAGES →` to read the negotiation thread (read-only for manager)
- Manager sees the full conversation context before deciding

