### 5.14 SAVINGS TRACKER — GLOBAL FEATURE

*Appears on: Officer Dashboard (right panel), Admin Dashboard, Admin Reports*

#### Logic
```
For each completed procurement cycle:
  savings = max(all quotes received) − actual PO value

Annual total = sum of all savings across all POs this year
Monthly trend = savings per month for last 12 months
```

#### Savings Widget Component (SavingsWidget.tsx)

Used in Officer right panel (compact) and Admin reports (full):

**Compact version (Officer Dashboard right panel):**
```
SAVINGS THIS YEAR
──────────────────
₹8,23,450
+₹45,000 from last PO

[VIEW BREAKDOWN →]
```
Number animates (counts up) when widget enters view.

**Full version (Admin Reports):**
```
VENDORA HAS SAVED YOUR ORGANIZATION

₹8,23,450 THIS YEAR

through competitive procurement


[Monthly savings chart — line chart, Recharts]
[Oct  Nov  Dec  Jan  Feb  Mar ...]
[₹45K ₹78K ₹1.2L ₹34K ₹92K ₹1.1L ...]
```

**Per-PO Breakdown Table:**
```
PO NUMBER    ITEM               HIGHEST QUOTE   PO VALUE    SAVED
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PO-2025-1203 Industrial Bearings  ₹1,12,500     ₹95,000    ₹17,500
PO-2025-1198 Office Supplies      ₹32,000       ₹26,000    ₹6,000
PO-2025-1185 Safety Equipment     ₹1,85,000     ₹1,45,000  ₹40,000
```
Table rows animate in staggered on mount.

When the page loads, the total number counts up from 0 to `₹8,23,450` over 2 seconds using requestAnimationFrame.

