## 7. NOTIFICATION SYSTEM

### Toast Notifications (react-hot-toast, custom styled)
All toasts are directional — they tell you what happened AND what comes next.

```
// Quote received
"↓ NEW QUOTE — RFQ #2847 · Mehta Industries · ₹95,000"

// Approval cleared
"✓ APPROVED — PO #1203 being generated now"

// Invoice sent
"✉ INVOICE SENT — INV-089 delivered to Mehta Industries"

// New message
"💬 NEW MESSAGE — RFQ #2847 · Ramesh Shah"
```

### Supabase Realtime Subscriptions
```typescript
// Subscribe to:
// - quotations table (new quotes → officer gets toast)
// - approvals table (status change → officer gets toast)
// - negotiation_messages table (new message → both parties get toast)
// - rfqs table (status change → vendor gets toast)
```

