## SUMMARY — WHAT MAKES VENDORA WIN

| Feature | Why Judges Stop |
|---|---|
| Video background login + role tiles | First 10 seconds sets the tone |
| Procurement Pipeline kanban | No other ERP visualizes workflow this way |
| Bloomberg-style comparison table | Looks like serious financial software |
| Weighted Decision Engine sliders | Feels intelligent, not just informational |
| Hold-to-Approve mechanic | Shows you understand real-world risk |
| Negotiation Thread with audit trail | Replaces the #1 pain point — WhatsApp |
| System messages in thread | Makes audit log human-readable |
| Savings Tracker with counting animation | Answers "what's the ROI?" in 2 seconds |
